          "Line 75: `const totalNetVotes = (restaurant.upvotes ?? 0) - (restaurant.downvotes ?? 0)` \u2014 Prisma schema defines upvotes and downvotes as non-nullable Int fields, so these values are guaranteed to be numbers. The `?? 0` is redundant."
