          "Lines 23, 26, 30, 33, 45: advance() is called at six transition points inside fetchWithFallback, silently mutating the POST handler's local state variable",
          "The function's return type is '{ results, state, empty, terms }' but the 'state' in the return is the function parameter's stale value, not the mutated caller state \u2014 it is unused at the call site (line 193)"
