          "app/api/search/route.ts calls triggerScrape() fire-and-forget when grouped.length < 3 (line 52-54). SearchPoller unconditionally fires POST /api/scrape on every mount (line 31). For low-results queries both fire concurrently \u2014 two scrape pipelines run for the same city+query. The upsertRestaurant deduplicates by name/address, preventing data corruption, but Reddit and Google Places API quota is wasted."
